After the last gig, Eldritch relocated to Hamburg, where he was later joined by Hussey to write the next album. This is stated clearly in Hussey's autobiography. However, Craig Adams did NOT join Hussey in Hamburg. Not only is this not stated in Hussey's autobiography, Hussey recalls the miserable time there with Aldritch, which would not have happened if Adams had also ben present.
